productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Lular has one of these. She works as a cake decorator and she says it looks ragged.
My macaroni penguin loves to play with it.
one of my hobbies is skydiving. and when i'm skydiving this works great.
My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
I tried to pepper it but got prune all over it.
